'''林祺堂（Lim Kay Tong; ''' 1954年-)，是一位资深的新加坡电影、电视及舞台剧演员。

== 早年 ==


父亲為放射科医生，希望兒子成为律师，但是支持他作梦想。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.esquiresingapore.com/Entertainment/Features/article/Lim-Kay-Tong|title=Lim Kay Tong|date=3 October 2014|publisher=Mongoose Publishing|accessdate=7 October 2014|agency=Esquire Singapore|last1=Cheong|first1=Wayne|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924002304/http://www.esquiresingapore.com/Entertainment/Features/article/Lim-Kay-Tong|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

早年在[[英华中学_(自主)|英华中学]]和在英格蘭的一所寄宿学校受過教育<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19740814-1.2.110.aspx|title=Schoolboy Ting in U-23 rugby team|date=14 August 1974|publisher=Singapore Press Holdings|accessdate=18 September 2014|agency=The Straits Times|last1=Robert|first1=Godfrey|archive-date=2016-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917034926/http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19740814-1.2.110.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19750708-1.2.111.19.aspx|title=Comeback by ex-stars Salleh and Foo|date=8 July 1975|publisher=Singapore Press Holdings|accessdate=18 September 2014|agency=The Straits Times|last1=Robert|first1=Godfrey|archive-date=2016-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916200447/http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19750708-1.2.111.19.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。在[[新加坡国民服役|服兵役]]的時候林祺堂在橄欖球上贏得了[[新加坡武裝部隊|新加坡武装部队]]色彩奖。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19750705-1.2.126.14.aspx|title=Supra is Forces' Sportsman of Year|date=5 July 1975|publisher=Singapore Press Holdings|accessdate=18 September 2014|agency=The Straits Times|archive-date=2016-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917033226/http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19750705-1.2.126.14.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1975年，林祺堂遷移到英格蘭的 [[东约克郡|东约克郡]]，在那裡進一步接受教育，隨後在1978年，他毕业于 [[赫爾大學|赫尔大学]]，他的導師是[[安东尼·明格拉|安东尼·明格拉]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/today20080409-1.2.44.2.aspx|title=Ten One|date=9 April 2008|publisher=MediaCorp|accessdate=19 September 2014|agency=TODAY|last1=Martin|first1=Mayo|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424053024/http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/today20080409-1.2.44.2.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。在1980年，他获得了[[伦敦|伦敦]]韦伯-道格拉斯戲劇藝術学院的文憑。
<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19821021-1.2.241.aspx|title=Talent night Best Actress Best Actor|date=21 October 1982|publisher=Singapore Press Holdings|accessdate=18 September 2014|agency=The Straits Times|last1=Abisheganaden|first1=Jacintha|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063019/http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19821021-1.2.241.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

